tpot = TPOTRegressor(
    scoring='neg_mean_absolute_error',
    max_time_mins=500,
    n_jobs=-1,
    verbosity=2,
    early_stop=10,
    warm_start=True,
    cv=10)
tpot.fit(X_train, y_train)
print(tpot.score(X_test, y_test))
